title: Jovani 60933 Fully beaded short dress
body_html:
• Closure: Invisible Back Zipper with Hook and Eye Closure.
     
  • Details: Fully beaded short dress, form fitting silhouette, cap sleeves, high neckline, closed back.
     
  • Fabric: 100% Polyester
  • Fit: The Model is 5'9" Wearing 3" Heels. 
  • Neckline: High
